pokedexEntries.gold: Although it looks frightening, it is actually kind and affectionate. It is very popular among women.
pokedexEntries.silver: It has an active, playful nature. Many women like to frolic with it because of its affectionate ways.
pokedexEntries.crystal: In truth, it is a cowardly Pokémon. It growls eagerly in order to hide its fear from its opponent.
pokedexEntries.ruby: By baring its fangs and making scary face, Snubbull sends smaller Pokémon scurrying away in terror. However, this Pokémon seems a little sad at making its foes flee.

pokedexEntries.sun: Despite its intimidating face, it's quite cowardly. Its desperate attempts to appear threatening make it popular with people.
pokedexEntries.moon: Its growls make its opponents uneasy. This laid-back Pokémon tends to sleep half the day.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: It grows close to others easily and is also easily spoiled. The disparity between its face and its actions makes many young people wild about it.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: In contrast to its appearance, it’s quite timid. When playing with other puppy Pokémon, it sometimes gets bullied.
